<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((صحيح الأدب)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٢٧)</span>: ق.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>